Any and all versions of the Software released prior to April 11, 2025, are licensed under the AllTheMons-ARR license, which can be found [here](https://docs.google.com/document/d/10j5-Z61m0Ox89Ky3WYGzhQoLxPfopZ08c2IqGhonV7A/edit?tab=t.0).

